Module scenebuilder.core
Package com.oracle.javafx.scenebuilder.core.fxom

Class FXOMNodes

java.lang.Object
com.oracle.javafx.scenebuilder.core.fxom.FXOMNodes
public class FXOMNodes
extends Object
This class groups static utility methods which operate on FXOMNode and subclasses (a bit like Collection and Collections).

  • Method Details

    • sort

      public static List<FXOMObject> sort​(Set<FXOMObject> objects)
      Sorts the specified set of objects according their location in the fxom document. Objets are sorted according depth first order. In particular, if objects all have the same parent, then the resulting list will be sorted by indexes.
      Parameters:
      objects - a set of fxom objects (never null but possibly empty)
      Returns:
      the list of objets sorted by position in the fxom document

    • flatten

      public static Set<FXOMObject> flatten​(Set<FXOMObject> objects)
      Flattens a set of fxom objects. A set of fxom objects is declared "flat" if each object member of the set has no ancestor member of the set.
      Parameters:
      objects - a set of fxom objects (never null)
      Returns:
      the flat set of objects.

    • lookupAncestor

      public static FXOMObject lookupAncestor​(FXOMObject obj, Set<FXOMObject> candidates)
      Returns null or the first ancestor of "obj" which belongs to "candidates".
      Parameters:
      obj - an fxom object (never null)
      candidates - a set of fxom object (not null and not empty)
      Returns:
      null or the first ancestor of "obj" which belongs to "candidates".
